00:18:39.200 --> 00:18:41.620
Megumi, kailangan kong kumalma ka.

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:44.530
Sa tingin ko may higit pa dito
kaysa sa tila.

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:46.220
Ngayon lahat tayo

00:18:47.010 --> 00:18:48.560
ay umaasa na ang Grand Duke ay gumising kaagad

00:18:49.070 --> 00:18:50.330
at muling namamahala.

00:18:50.350 --> 00:18:51.490
Bakit kahit sino

00:18:51.590 --> 00:18:54.140
gusto mong lasunin ang punong surgeon ng Grand Duke
?

