Maganda ang ginawa mo.

00:34:38.750 --> 00:34:39.500
Nakalulungkot,

00:34:40.710 --> 00:34:42.730
Sinubukan ko ng maraming beses noon

00:34:42.750 --> 00:34:43.650
ngunit nabigo.

